# Platform AI (ArtifactGraph MCP)

- This repository builds the standalone `artifactgraph` MCP; it is not a
  product docs/code hub.
- Do not keep `platform-repos.json` or cross-repository topology here.
- Package source, graph tools, installers, owned harness, tests, and release
  docs are the scope; see `/platform-ai`.
- Runtime binds directly to the product root where `artifactgraph init` ran.
- Product registries remain product-local; never depend on sibling checkout
  layout or copy another MCP's harness.
